title: Super Mega Worm v1.0.8 [PD]
description:
Mother Earth is on the brink of extinction and has released her last defense, the Great Death Worm, Wojira. Wojira is on a revenge mission to destroy all the Human parasites. 

Crawl and eat your way through waves of humans and their robots of destruction. Grow and evolve into the ultimate weapon of destruction. You are the last line of defense, can you save the world?

Features:

- Super fun, fast and furious Gameplay 
- Awesome Retro Art Style 
- 24 Action Packed Levels 
- 2 Different Game Modes 
- 3 Destructive Super Abilities 
- 2 Different Control Schemes 
- 20 Delicious Items to Eat 
- Leaderboards and Achievements
- Tablet Support

What's New:

Ver.1.0.8
- Fix for black screen on start up.
